msg: Fix a NULL dereference core dump in svn_error_purge_tracing() if an
error chain with only tracing errors is passed to it.
One should never be passed in, as it makes no sense to have no true
error but tracing, but if one is passed to svn_error_purge_tracing(),
it's better to have SVN_ERR_ASSERT() called than get a core dump.
